Name: Reimu fumo
Description: In the mystical land of Gensokyo, Reimu Hakurei serves as the shrine maiden of the Hakurei Shrine, maintaining the boundary between the human and youkai worlds. Despite her lazy demeanor and constant complaints about lack of donations, she's incredibly powerful and efficient at resolving supernatural incidents with her yin-yang orbs and ability to float.

ConsumeProperties.UseText: You have eaten Reimu, r u ok bro?
